<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">三　長老之譬喻二</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十四　輸毘多品</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四〇　巴羅大耶迦（果施）</cb:mulu><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.170" type="PTS_hide"></ref><cb:div type="other">
<milestone unit="juan" n="15"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0234a" n="0234a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">第十五　奢達品</cb:mulu><head>第十五　奢達品</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四一　阿第奢提耶（上傘蓋）</cb:mulu><head>一四一　阿第奢提耶（上傘蓋）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a0601">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0234a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>阿塔達西佛，至其涅槃時，傘蓋層層作，奉獻塔婆上。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a0701">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0234a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>時時常來此，南無師塔婆，吾於傘蓋上，奉獻眾花覆。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a0801">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0234a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>一千七百劫，吾做諸神王，供養塔婆果，吾不生人世。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a0901">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0234a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a1001" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿第奢提耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四二　單巴羅巴迦（柱載）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.171"></ref>一四二　單巴羅巴迦（柱載）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a1301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0234a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間之救主，單摩達西滅，尊佛勝支提，吾運載幡柱。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0234a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0234a1401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0234a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>並再作階梯，登上勝塔婆，吾採素馨花，捧獻立柱上。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0235a" n="0235a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a0101">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a0101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>諸佛並諸法，尊師吾成滿，惡趣吾不知，供養塔婆果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a0201">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a0201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>九十四劫昔，其名稱塔頂<note n="0235001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Thūpasikha（塔頂）。</note>，大力十六人，有為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a0301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者單巴羅巴迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四三　耶提伽羅迦（欄楯造）</cb:mulu><head>一四三　耶提伽羅迦（欄楯造）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a1001">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間之救主，毘耶達西滅，心淨吾欣喜，為佛作欄楯。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a1101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>圍繞此摩尼，吾為最上祭，吾作欄楯祭，當場吾死逝。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a1201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>諸神與人間，吾生任何胎，虛空持摩尼<note n="0235001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">讀為 Maṇiṁ（暹羅本）。</note>，積福此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a1301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>一千六百劫，名喚摩尼光<note n="0235002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Maṇippabha（摩尼光）。</note>，大力三十二，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0235a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0235a1401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0235a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0236a" n="0236a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a0101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者耶提伽羅迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四四　薩巴利瓦利耶（有隨眾）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.172"></ref>一四四　薩巴利瓦利耶（有隨眾）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0236a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>巴多穆塔拉，彼為最勝者，如火塊熾燃，正覺尊涅槃。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0236a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>大雄臨寂滅，塔婆世廣聞，尊佛身骨上，人崇施塔婆<note n="0236001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">依異本及暹羅本讀為 thūpadattaṁ。</note>。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0236a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>心淨吾欣喜，吾作金欄楯，香氣飄彌漫<note n="0236002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">依暹羅本讀為 dhūpagandho 但如底本讀 ca 為 va（異本），意為「如天翔之煙塊」。</note>，相應時塔婆。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0236a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>諸神與人間，無論生何處，依昔此果報，不見下劣性。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0236a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>千五百劫昔，其名喚成就<note n="0236003" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">應讀 Samatta（成就）（暹羅本及其他異本）。</note>，其數有八人，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a1301">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0236a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0236a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0236a1401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者薩巴利瓦利耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0237a" n="0237a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四五　溫瑪普毘耶（亞麻花）</cb:mulu><head>一四五　溫瑪普毘耶（亞麻花）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0237a0801">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0237a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>尊貴彼世尊，受尊供物人，悉達多寂滅，供佛大塔婆。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0237a0901">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0237a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>悉達多大仙，於時之葬祭，吾持亞麻花，奉獻至塔婆。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0237a1001">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0237a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依此獻花供，九十四劫間，吾不知惡趣，供養塔婆果。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0237a1101">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0237a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>第九劫往昔，名蘇摩提婆<note n="0237001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Somadeva（蘇摩神）。</note>，八十五大力，有為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0237a1201">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0237a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0237a1301" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者溫瑪普毘耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0237a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0238a" n="0238a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a02"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四六　阿努樓瑪達耶迦（相應布施）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.173"></ref>一四六　阿努樓瑪達耶迦（相應布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a0501">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0238a0501" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>阿諾瑪達西，作欄繞提樹，吾以手作業，布施泥灰漿。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a0601">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0238a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>阿諾瑪達西，注目此善業，佛立僧眾中，述說如次偈：</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a0701">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0238a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「依此泥漿業，更依心意願，享受無虧樂，得致彼苦滅。」</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a0801">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0238a0801" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>面色既清淨，安靜心鎮定，等正覺者教，吾保最後身。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a09"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a0901">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0238a0901" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>由今茲一劫，無虧滿百劫，名喚全堅塊<note n="0238001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Sabbagghana（金堅塊）。</note>，大力轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a10"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a1001">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0238a1001" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0238a1101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者阿努樓瑪達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a13"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0238a14"/>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0239a" n="0239a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a01"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四七　瑪格達耶迦（道施）</cb:mulu><head>一四七　瑪格達耶迦（道施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a0301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0239a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>由河水中出，具眼往森林，嚴相悉達多，吾見正覺者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a0401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0239a0401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>執持鋤與籠，其行道不平，頂禮拜尊師，己心得清淨。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a0501">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0239a0501" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>當時作此業，九十四劫間，惡趣吾不知，施道此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a0601">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0239a0601" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>五十七劫昔，出世一人王，其名謂善覺<note n="0239001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Suppabuddha（善覺）。</note>，統人領導者。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a07"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a0701">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0239a0701" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a08"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a0801" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者瑪格達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a12"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四八　巴羅伽達耶迦（板布施）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.174"></ref>一四八　巴羅伽達耶迦（板布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0239a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0239a1401">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0239a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾業製乘具，巧明木工匠，手作旃檀板，布施世緣者。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0240a" n="0240a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a0101">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a0101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>天宮黃金造，佳構常輝耀，象馬等座騎，神之乘物具。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a0201">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a0201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>轎輿高臺閣，隨欲得生來，寶玉吾無數<note n="0240001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">akkhobiṇī 解為（Skt, akṣanhiṇī）之意。</note>，施板此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a0301">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>吾之施此板，九十一劫間，惡趣吾不知，布施板果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a0401">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a0401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>五十七劫昔，四人有化作<note n="0240002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Bhavanimmita（有化作）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a05"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a0501">六</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a0501" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a0601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是巴羅伽達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a10"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a11"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一四九　瓦單薩奇耶（頭飾）</cb:mulu><head>一四九　瓦單薩奇耶（頭飾）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a1301">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>名稱須彌陀，自存無敵者，於委身孤獨，行入大森林。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0240a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0240a1401">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0240a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>香樹花開滿<note n="0240001-1" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">salaḷa 香樹之一種。</note>，編結作頭飾，指向世導師，吾獻彼尊佛。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0241a" n="0241a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a0101">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a0101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>捧獻彼花朶，從此三萬劫，吾不知惡趣，供佛此果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a0201">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a0201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>千九百劫昔，化作十六人<note n="0241002" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Nimmita（化作）。</note>，大力具七寶，有為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a03"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a0301">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a0301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a04"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a0401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者瓦單薩奇耶長老宣唱此等偈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a06"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a07"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a08"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a09"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">一五〇　巴蘭伽達耶迦（座椅布施）</cb:mulu><head><ref cRef="PTS.Ap.175"></ref>一五〇　巴蘭伽達耶迦（座椅布施）</head>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a11"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a1101">一</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a1101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>世間居上首，須彌陀世尊，吾施其座椅，座椅層層疊。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a12"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a1201">二</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a1201" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>請知吾心意，爾時常為吾，具有七種寶，座椅為吾生。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a13"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a1301">三</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a1301" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>依此施座椅，從此三萬劫，惡趣吾不知，施座椅果報。</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0241a14"/><p xml:id="pN29p0241a1401">四</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0241a1401" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>二萬劫往昔，黃金光三人<note n="0241001" resp="NanChuan" place="foot text" type="orig">Suvaṇṇābha（黃金光）。</note>，大力具七寶，出為轉輪王。</l></lg>
<pb ed="N" xml:id="N29.0017.0242a" n="0242a"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a01"/><p xml:id="pN29p0242a0101">五</p><lg xml:id="lgN29p0242a0101" type="abnormal" style="margin-left:3em"><l>四種無礙解……</l></lg>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a02"/><p xml:id="pN29p0242a0201" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">——如是尊者巴蘭伽達耶迦長老宣唱此等偈。</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a03"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a04"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a05"/>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a06"/><p xml:id="pN29p0242a0601" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">攝頌：</p>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a07"/><lg xml:id="lgN29p0242a0701" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:3em">奢達、單巴與耶提、巴利瓦羅、溫瑪普毘耶、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a08"/><l style="text-indent:3em">阿努樓瑪、瑪格達伊、巴羅達伊、瓦單薩迦、</l>
<lb ed="N" n="0242a09"/><l style="text-indent:3em">巴蘭伽達耶、十人說此五十六偈。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
